# Next.js Template Project Overview

This is a modern Next.js 13+ template with the following key features:

## Core Files
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with theme and internationalization setup
- [middleware.ts](mdc:middleware.ts) - Next.js middleware for handling routing and auth
- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration
-

## Key Directories
- `app/` - Next.js app router pages and components
- `i18n/` - Internationalization configuration and translations
- `providers/` - React context providers
- `hooks/` - Custom React hooks
- `types/` - TypeScript type definitions
- `prisma/` - Prisma ORM schema and migrations
- `supabase/` - Supabase configuration and types
- `db/` - The implementation of all atomic operations in the database.

## Features
- TypeScript support
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Dark mode support via next-themes
- Internationalization with next-intl
- Database integration ready (Prisma & Supabase)
- Form handling with react-hook-form and zod

- Authentication ready with Supabase Auth